---
// Mission section - Who we are - staggered/overlapping editorial layout
---

<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-cream relative">
  <div class="container-wide">
    <!-- Section intro -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-20">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 reveal">
        <span class="label-sm text-terracotta mb-4 block">Uber uns</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display text-charcoal leading-[1.05]">
          Wer wir<br/>
          <span class="italic text-sage-dark">sind</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:pt-8 reveal" style="animation-delay: 100ms">
        <p class="text-xl text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
          GeTu Prospects e.V. ist ein interkultureller Verein in Berlin.
          Seit 2014 setzen wir uns fur Menschen aller Kulturen ein -
          geprÃ¤gt von christlichen Werten und dem Glauben an das Potenzial
          jedes Einzelnen.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Overlapping image/content layout -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Background image - full width -->
      <div class="relative lg:absolute lg:left-0 lg:top-0 lg:bottom-0 lg:w-7/12 reveal">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517486808906-6ca8b3f04846?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Community gathering"
          class="w-full h-[400px] lg:h-full object-cover"
        />
        <!-- Year badge -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 bg-terracotta p-6 text-white">
          <span class="block text-4xl font-display">2014</span>
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">Gegrundet</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content card - overlapping -->
      <div class="relative lg:ml-auto lg:w-6/12 lg:py-16">
        <div class="bg-charcoal text-white p-8 lg:p-12 reveal" style="animation-delay: 200ms">
          <div class="max-w-lg">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl lg:text-3xl mb-6">
              Unsere Vision
            </h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Eine Gesellschaft, in der jeder Mensch wertgeschatzt, unterstutzt
              und befahigt wird, sein volles Potenzial zu entfalten. Eine
              Gemeinschaft voller Verbundenheit, Wurde und Sinn.
            </p>

            <!-- Values grid -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
              <div>
                <div class="text-terracotta-light font-display text-2xl mb-1">01</div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Gemeinschaft</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Zusammenhalt starken</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-terracotta-light font-display text-2xl mb-1">02</div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Vielfalt</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Kulturen verbinden</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-terracotta-light font-display text-2xl mb-1">03</div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Perspektive</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Wege eroffnen</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-terracotta-light font-display text-2xl mb-1">04</div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Engagement</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Ehrenamtlich wirken</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <a href="/ueber-uns" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-10 text-terracotta-light hover:text-white transition-colors">
              Mehr uber uns
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
